'''T.J. Frame''' is an artist who provided many concept sketches for [[Star Wars: Episode III Revenge of the Sith|''Star Wars'': Episode III ''Revenge of the Sith'']]. He is also credited as a member of the Art team for ''[[Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic II: The Sith Lords]]''.

